00:33:37,573 --> 00:33:40,095
That is Jeff Lee, although obviously it's a comic

668
00:33:40,095 --> 00:33:41,256
or cartoon version.

669
00:33:41,256 --> 00:33:44,939
This is taken from the flyer for Us Versus Them,

670
00:33:44,939 --> 00:33:47,341
which is actually the second game that I did for Gottlieb.

671
00:33:47,341 --> 00:33:49,563
But this is the actual Jeff Lee,

672
00:33:49,563 --> 00:33:53,686
back in the day, taken from a video.

