00:34:02,813 --> 00:34:03,594
But...

678
00:34:05,455 --> 00:34:08,698
When I'm gone, somebody will unearth it.

679
00:34:08,698 --> 00:34:12,761
Anyway, interesting thing here is on the thing,

680
00:34:12,761 --> 00:34:15,122
Chris Brewer was one of our programmers

681
00:34:15,122 --> 00:34:18,545
and also did art as well, very talented.

682
00:34:18,545 --> 00:34:20,947
And he made a calendar, he made a Cubert calendar.

683
00:34:20,947 --> 00:34:23,909
He also made a thing called the Cubert Coloring Book,

684
00:34:23,909 --> 00:34:28,172
which had different characters,

685
00:34:28,172 --> 00:34:32,155
like Jacques Cousteau with Qs, you know.

686
00:34:32,155 --> 00:34:33,035
Anyway.

687
00:34:35,839 --> 00:34:36,639
Let's move on.

